---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Damian Zakrzewski | Bioinformatics">
	<!-- Zmniejszyliśmy mt-20 na mt-4, żeby zlikwidować wielką dziurę -->
	<main class="mt-4">
		
		<!-- Hero Section / About -->
		<section id="about" class="mb-24">
			<h1 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond'] italic text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-900 mb-10 tracking-wide leading-tight">
				Bridging the gap between computational models and wet-lab reality.
			</h1>
			
			<div class="max-w-2xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-sm sm:text-base">
				<p>
					I am a 6th-semester bioinformatics student at Poznań University of Technology. 
					My primary research interests revolve around <strong>RNA folding and structural biology</strong>. 
					I thrive at the intersection of computer science and biology, actively working to translate 
					dry-lab predictions into tangible wet-lab experiments.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					Currently, I am involved in several cross-disciplinary projects:
				</p>

				<ul class="space-y-5 mt-6 mb-8 pl-1">
					
					<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300 flex-shrink-0"></span>
						<p>
							<strong>RNA Structure Analysis:</strong> Lead author of the <a href="https://rnabridge.cs.put.poznan.pl" target="_blank" class="underline decoration-slate-200 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-slate-900 transition-colors">RNABridge</a> web application under the supervision of Prof. M. Antczak and Prof. T. Żok <em>(Publication in preparation, pre-submission to JMB)</em>.
						</p>
					</li>
					
					<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300 flex-shrink-0"></span>
						<p>
							<strong>Materials Chemistry:</strong> Synthesizing and modifying Metal-Organic Frameworks (TMU-16 and TMU-16 NH₂) at Adam Mickiewicz University in collaboration with Prof. J. Gościańska and Dr. Ejsmont.
						</p>
					</li>
					
					<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
						<span class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300 flex-shrink-0"></span>
						<p>
							<strong>Chemical Technology:</strong> Providing computational and research support at the PUT Faculty of Chemical Technology under the guidance of Dr. Grzywaczyk.
						</p>
					</li>

				</ul>

				<p class="pt-2">
					Beyond the laboratory, I serve as the administrator for the <a href="http://solardynamics.put.poznan.pl" target="_blank" class="underline decoration-slate-200 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-slate-900 transition-colors">SolarDynamics</a> scientific club, fostering collaboration and innovation within the student community.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="research" class="mb-32">
			<!-- Tutaj będziemy budować projekty -->
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
